}

vars {
  baseUrl: http://localhost:3001
  email: admin@metaplatform.com
  password: admin123
}

docs {
  # MetaPlatform API Collection

  A complete collection of all ~140 API endpoints, organized by section.

  ## Setup

  1. Open Bruno (https://usebruno.com)
  2. Import this collection: `File → Open Collection → select bruno/MetaPlatform/`
  3. Set environment to `Local Dev` (auto-detected)

  ## Sections

  - Auth           — login, refresh, /me
  - Health         — /api/health
  - Storage        — PG / Neo4j / ES / MinIO / Kafka
  - AI             — Embeddings, LLM, Agent, RAG, OCR
  - Analytics      — ClickHouse, NL2SQL, CDC, Quality, Simulator
  - Observability  — Metrics, Logs, Traces, Audit
  - Notifications  — In-app, Email, WebSocket
  - Scheduler      — Cron jobs
  - Apps           — Application management
  - Ontology       — Object types, attributes, relations
  - Processes      — BPMN instances, tasks
  - Knowledge      — Documents, search, RAG
  - Agents         — AI agent workspace
  - Admin          — Users, orgs, billing, plugins
  - Market         — Apps, agents, templates, APIs

  All authenticated endpoints expect `Authorization: Bearer <token>` — get one
  via the Auth > Login request.
}